            <h2 class="text-headline brutalist-text mb-6">
              HIGH-CONVERTING<br />
              BUSINESS WEBSITES
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Professional websites designed to convert visitors into customers. 
              Proven layouts that drive results for your business.
            </p>
